#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.154"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.154:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:0.2"
msgid "15. Diṭṭhivagga "
msgstr "15. Views "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 154. Micchādiṭṭhisutta → micchā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.154:0.3"
msgid "154. Micchādiṭṭhisutta "
msgstr "154. Wrong View "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.185, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.2"
msgid "“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa micchādiṭṭhi uppajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does wrong view arise?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.3"
msgid "Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe … "
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.4"
msgid "“rūpe kho, bhikkhave, sati, rūpaṃ upādāya, rūpaṃ abhinivissa micchādiṭṭhi uppajjati. "
msgstr "“When form exists, because of grasping form and insisting on form, wrong view arises. "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.5"
msgid "Vedanāya sati … "
msgstr "When feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.6"
msgid "saññāya sati … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.7"
msgid "saṅkhāresu sati … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.8"
msgid "viññāṇe sati, viññāṇaṃ upādāya, viññāṇaṃ abhinivissa micchādiṭṭhi uppajjati. "
msgstr "consciousness exists, because of grasping consciousness and insisting on consciousness, wrong view arises. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.9"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.10"
msgid "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is form permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.11"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.12"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.13"
msgid "api nu taṃ anupādāya micchādiṭṭhi uppajjeyyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But by not grasping what’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable, would wrong view arise?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.14"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.15"
msgid "“Vedanā … "
msgstr "“Is feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.16"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.17"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.18"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "consciousness permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.19"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.20"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.21"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.22"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, api nu taṃ anupādāya micchādiṭṭhi uppajjeyyā”ti? "
msgstr "“But by not grasping what’s impermanent, suffering, and perishable, would wrong view arise?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.23"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.24"
msgid "“Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "“Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.154:1.25"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.154:1.26"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

